data.description: Inspiring rural property nestled upon 2.7 acres on a quiet country cul-de-sac road. This inviting home promises unsurpassed views with generous space for living and entertaining. The home features expansive hardwood floors, extra room for a home office, custom barn doors and a beautifully updated kitchen that includes a farmhouse style kitchen sink, tile backsplash and butcher block countertops. The private master bedroom retreat will not disappoint with a full tile surround walk-in shower, separate tub, dual vanities and a sweeping walk-in closet. Huge, ground level in-law suite, fully finished with a separate entrance. New SOLAR, HVAC and Minisplit installed. Solar is owned and includes a 25 year warranty. All appliances and security systems included. 50 x 30 heated shop with a lift and plenty of room for all your toys! Lush shade trees, fruit trees, mature landscaping, grapevines, large garden area, frost free hydrants, 20 x 10 garden shed and endless hours of swing set fun!
